So blessed to have been touched by this beautiful family... Here, i was provided with three different photos.  I was asked to create a portrait based on those images to bring a family together. As they did not have an opportunity in the hospital to create this special moment. . .

Today I saw my baby grow up right in front of my eyes...childhood is a blink of an eye. I feel as though today was a lifetime of memories all wrapped up into one day. Can't  stop feeling that you should "feel" all life moments, before they become memories. Bitter sweet indeed, myself being crushed...but at the same time, it's been the proudest day in my life.
